parameters: Polka: "Finally, we can talk just the two of us, \n[6]."
\n[6]: "The doll is talking? What's this?"
Polka: "Hehe, everyone has that kind of reaction, don't they?"
Polka: "I'm Polka, don't be surprised and just listen."
Polka: "The true identity of Pony-Celes is Morisaki Yui."
Polka: "I'm the one who made her into Pony-Celes."

Polka: "With that look, I guess you had your suspicions. She doesn't
seem to be good at hiding things."
\n[6]: "...I had my doubts, but I couldn't be certain."

\n[6]: "Why did you make Yui into Pony-Celes! To give her such a
dangerous role..."

Polka: "It's understandable that you're angry. But only Yui-chan can
do it. She understands that as well."

Polka: "And now, she's fighting of her own will. You can blame me, but
please understand why she's fighting."
\n[6]: "Even so..."
Polka: "Sorry, but we're out of time."

Polka: "It would be bad if Yui-chan came back now. I want to keep this
conversation a secret between you and me."
Polka: "She would definitely oppose involving you, \n[6]."
Polka: "Shall we continue the conversation?"

\n[6]: "I'm not convinced, but I guess I have no choice but to
listen..."
Polka: "Thank you, \n[6]. Then, I'll put it simply."

Polka: "I'm going to enter a long sleep. During that time, I want you
to support Yui-chan from the shadows in my place."
Polka: "That's all... but it's the most difficult thing."

\n[6]: "We're supposed to fight Zaidrag, and you're going to sleep?
That's too convenient for you!"

Polka: "It's to accumulate the power needed to seal the ruler of
Zaidrag, Dargnoa."

Polka: "The method to seal Dargnoa is the ultimate magic, Holy
Resurrection. This magic requires a tremendous amount of power to
activate."

Polka: "I have to reduce my life functions to the minimum and convert
it into power before Dargnoa fully revives."
\n[6]: "If that magic is completed, can we definitely seal Dargnoa?"
Polka: "Yes, that's right. But it will cost my life..."
\n[6]: "Then, Polka, you will..."

Polka: "Of course I'll die. Well, it's a life I lost a long time ago
anyway, so it doesn't really matter."

Polka: "The problem is that if I don't regain the power to use the
ultimate magic, we can't defeat Dargnoa."

Polka: "Yui-chan will challenge Dargnoa without knowing this and will
be defeated..."

Polka: "Even if she knows she can't win, Yui-chan will still fight
Dargnoa. That's just the kind of girl she is..."
\n[6]: "Understood... I'll support Yui. I'll definitely protect her."

\n[6]: "So promise me, no matter what happens, never teach her that
magic."
\n[6]: "That's my condition."

Polka: "Of course. I promise. Besides... I never intended to teach
Yui-chan in the first place."
Polka: "Sealing Dargnoa is my role alone."

\n[6]: "Peace at the cost of Polka's life... Sorry. But I want Yui to
live. I don't want her to die."
Polka: "Hehe, you're a kind person too."

Polka: "It's about time for me to go to sleep. I'm counting on you,
\n[6]."

Polka: "And please, make sure you never tell Yui-chan about this
magic."
\n[6]: "Understood..."
